{"id":5,"text":"SURESH BABU VENKATESAN\nCloud Data Architect | 14+ Years\n\nSan Jose, CA | suresh.babu@cloudarch.io | +1 (408) 555-0177\nlinkedin.com\/in\/sureshbabu-arch | github.com\/sbabu\n\n14+ Years Exp | 15 Certifications | 10K+ GitHub Stars | AWS Hero 2023\n\nPROFESSIONAL SUMMARY\n\nCloud Data Architect with 14 years designing petabyte-scale data platforms across AWS, Azure, and GCP for technology, e-commerce, and media companies. Thought leader in multi-cloud data architecture, lakehouse design, and real-time streaming. Architect of platforms collectively serving 1B+ users globally. AWS Hero, Google Cloud Champion with 15 certifications. Active Apache Iceberg PMC Member and open-source contributor with 10,000+ GitHub stars across data engineering projects.\n\nSKILLS & EXPERTISE\n\nData Formats: Apache Iceberg, Apache Hudi, Delta Lake, Parquet, ORC, Avro, Protobuf, Arrow  \nStreaming: Kafka, Apache Flink, Spark Streaming, Samza, Kinesis, Pub\/Sub, Dataflow  \nQuery Engines: Trino, Presto, Spark SQL, BigQuery, Athena, Snowflake, Databricks SQL, ClickHouse  \nLanguages: Python, Java, Scala, Go, SQL, PySpark, R, Bash, TypeScript, Terraform, Helm  \nCloud AWS: S3, Redshift, Glue, Lambda, EMR, Athena, SQS, CloudWatch, SageMaker, Lake Formation  \nCloud GCP: BigQuery, Dataflow, Pub\/Sub, Vertex AI, Bigtable, Spanner, Cloud Run, Composer  \nCloud Azure: ADLS Gen2, Synapse Analytics, Azure Purview, Databricks, Event Hubs, AML  \nOpen Source: Apache Iceberg PMC Member, Kafka contributor, dbt tools  \n\nPROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE\n\nPRINCIPAL CLOUD DATA ARCHITECT | Netflix | 2022 - Present\n\nClient: Netflix | Media Streaming, Content Analytics, Data Platform\n\nDesigned next-gen content analytics on AWS processing 500B+ daily streaming events from 230M+ global subscribers using Kafka, Flink, and Apache Iceberg.  \nArchitected multi-region active-active data lake using Apache Iceberg and S3 achieving zero RPO\/RTO.  \nLed migration to Apache Flink + Kafka reducing latency from hours to seconds.  \nBuilt real-time analytics platform delivering KPIs to product teams.  \nDesigned self-service data platform for 1,000+ analysts.  \nCreated global data mesh with 50+ domain data products.  \nLed team of 15 architects.  \nReduced AWS costs by $8M annually.  \nDeveloped open-source iceberg-tools (3,500+ GitHub stars).  \n\nEnv: AWS, Kafka, Apache Flink, Apache Iceberg, Trino, Python, Scala, Databricks, dbt, Terraform, Spark  \n\n---\n\nSENIOR DATA ARCHITECT | Google Cloud | 2018 - 2022\n\nClient: Google | Cloud Infrastructure, ML Platform\n\nDesigned GCP architectures for BigQuery, Dataflow, Pub\/Sub used by 5,000+ customers.  \nBuilt ML training platform processing 10PB+ datasets.  \nArchitected YouTube analytics pipeline processing 500M+ events daily.  \nLed enterprise architecture engagements.  \nCreated certification content and training courses.  \n\nEnv: BigQuery, Dataflow, Pub\/Sub, Bigtable, Spanner, Vertex AI, Python, Java, Terraform  \n\n---\n\nDATA ARCHITECT | Uber Technologies | 2015 - 2018\n\nClient: Uber | Real-Time Analytics\n\nDesigned real-time analytics processing 50M+ events daily.  \nBuilt analytics systems for 300+ cities.  \nCreated identity graph for 100M+ users.  \nLed migration to Hudi on S3.  \n\nEnv: Kafka, Flink, AWS S3, Presto, Hive, Python, Java, Scala, Spark  \n\n---\n\nSR. DATA ENGINEER | LinkedIn | 2013 - 2015\n\nClient: LinkedIn | Analytics\n\nBuilt pipeline processing 3B+ daily events.  \nDeveloped advertiser analytics platform.  \n\nEnv: Kafka, Samza, Hadoop, Hive, Python, Java  \n\n---\n\nCERTIFICATIONS\n\nAWS Solutions Architect Professional  \nAzure Solutions Architect Expert  \nAWS Data Analytics Specialty  \nSnowflake SnowPro Advanced Data Engineer  \nAWS Machine Learning Specialty  \nDatabricks Certified Data Engineer Professional  \nAWS DevOps Professional  \nConfluent Certified Developer for Kafka  \nGCP Professional Data Engineer  \nCKA Certified Kubernetes Administrator  \nGCP Professional Cloud 