ateral movement.  \nLed $120M security transformation program including SIEM modernization and PAM deployment.  \nHandled 4 nation-state intrusion attempts with zero data loss.  \nAchieved ISO 27001, PCI DSS Level 1, and SOC2 Type II certifications.  \n\n---\n\nDirector of Threat Intelligence  \nBooz Allen Hamilton – McLean, VA  \nJun 2016 – Mar 2021  \n\nLed classified threat intelligence programs supporting DoD and DHS.  \nBuilt APT attribution capability using HUMINT and SIGINT.  \nAuthored intelligence reports used in Congressional testimony.  \nDirected 12 major incident response engagements.  \nDeveloped ML-based malware classification system with 97.2% accuracy.  \n\n---\n\nSenior Cybersecurity Analyst  \nDepartment of Homeland Security (CISA) – Washington, DC  \nAug 2010 – May 2016  \n\nWorked in NCCIC as senior analyst handling national cybersecurity incidents.  \nAnalyzed 200+ major cyber incidents including ICS\/SCADA attacks.  \nCo-developed ICS-CERT vulnerability disclosure framework.  \n\n---\n\nCONTRIBUTIONS\n\nBoard Member – National Cybersecurity Alliance (2022–Present)  \nAdjunct Professor – Georgetown University  \nAuthor – \"Zero Trust in Practice\" (Wiley, 2021)  \nRSA Conference Keynote Speaker (2022, 2023)  ","label":[[0,12,"PERSON_NAME"],[68,92,"EMAIL"],[102,120,"PHONE_NUMBER"],[131,146,"LOCATION"],[157,191,"LINKEDIN"],[284,287,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[737,751,"SKILL"],[754,769,"SKILL"],[772,777,"SKILL"],[779,795,"SKILL"],[838,846,"SKILL"],[849,861,"SKILL"],[864,868,"SKILL"],[876,882,"SKILL"],[883,890,"SKILL"],[891,897,"SKILL"],[898,905,"SKILL"],[938,943,"CERTIFICATION"],[955,960,"CERTIFICATION"],[970,995,"CERTIFICATION"],[998,1014,"CERTIFICATION"],[1017,1039,"CERTIFICATION"],[1084,1100,"SKILL"],[1119,1144,"DEGREE"],[1147,1174,"UNIVERSITY"],[1175,1182,"GRADUATION_YEAR"],[1183,1205,"DEGREE"],[1207,1229,"UNIVERSITY"],[1232,1236,"GRADUATION_YEAR"],[1332,1335,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[1468,1487,"JOB_TITLE"],[1490,1512,"COMPANY_NAME"],[1515,1527,"LOCATION"