{"id":7,"text":"VENKAT KRISHNA REDDY\n\nData Platform Engineer – Real-Time Systems – 12+ Years Experience\n\nEmail: venkat.reddy@dataplatform.io  \nPhone: +1 (469) 555-0811  \nLocation: Plano, TX  \nLinkedIn: linkedin.com\/in\/venkatreddy  \nGitHub: github.com\/vkreddy  \n\n12+ Years Experience | 40+ Data Pipelines\n\n---\n\nPROFESSIONAL PROFILE\n\nData Platform Engineer specializing in building enterprise streaming architectures, lakehouse platforms, and developer-friendly data infrastructure at scale. 12+ years experience at top technology companies including Microsoft, Adobe, and Expedia. Expert in Apache Kafka, Apache Flink, Databricks, Delta Lake, and Snowflake. Known for building self-service data platforms that reduce time-to-insight from months to hours. Author of open-source Kafka utilities with 2,000+ GitHub stars.\n\n---\n\nWORK HISTORY\n\nSTAFF DATA PLATFORM ENGINEER – Microsoft (Azure Data)  \nRedmond, WA  \n2022 – Present  \n\nDesigned Azure-native lakehouse architecture on ADLS Gen2, Azure Synapse, and Delta Lake serving 10,000+ internal users.  \nBuilt event streaming platform on Azure Event Hubs processing 10B+ daily events.  \nDeveloped data catalog using Azure Purview covering 500,000+ datasets.  \nCreated developer platform enabling teams to deploy pipelines without infrastructure knowledge.  \nReduced Azure costs by 50% through optimization strategies.  \nImplemented Delta Live Tables for 50+ real-time pipelines.  \nBuilt ML feature platform on Azure ML.  \nDesigned Snowflake architecture for 500+ enterprise customers.  \n\nEnvironment: Azure ADLS, Event Hubs, Synapse, Azure Purview, Databricks, Delta Lake, Python, PySpark, dbt, Terraform, Azure ML, Snowflake  \n\n---\n\nSENIOR DATA ENGINEER – Adobe (Experience Platform)  \nSan Jose, CA  \n2018 – 2022  \n\nBuilt real-time customer data platform processing 500M+ daily events using Kafka and Apache Flink.  \nDeveloped segmentation engine using Flink CEP with 500ms latency.  \nArchitected data lake