{"id":12,"text":"DEVRAJ PATEL\n\nPRINCIPAL DATA ARCHITECT | ML ENGINEERING LEADER | 14+ YEARS\n\ndevraj.patel@datacraft.io\n+1 (214) 555-0391\nDallas, TX\nlinkedin.com\/in\/devrajpatel\ngithub.com\/devrajpatel\n\n14+ Years Experience\n$35M TCO Savings\n100+ Engineers Led\n5 Industries\n\n\nEXECUTIVE SUMMARY\n\nPrincipal Data Architect and ML Engineering Leader with 14 years delivering enterprise data transformation programs for financial services, healthcare, and logistics companies.\n\nExpert in designing scalable cloud-native data architectures on Snowflake, AWS, and Azure that support AI\/ML at scale.\n\nTrack record leading 100+ engineer data platform teams, managing $30M+ budgets, and achieving $50M+ in annual cost savings.\n\nRecognized speaker at Strata, DataCouncil, and Snowflake Summit.\n\nOpen-source contributor with dbt and Kafka tools.\n\n\nPROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE\n\nPRINCIPAL DATA ARCHITECT\nWells Fargo | Charlotte, NC | Feb 2021 - Present\n\nClient: Wells Fargo\nDomain: Financial Services, Regulatory Compliance\n\n- Defined 5-year enterprise data strategy migrating 3,000+ workloads from Teradata to Snowflake with $35M savings.\n- Established DataOps platform using dbt, GitHub Actions, Airflow enabling fast deployments with 99.9% reliability.\n- Designed real-time regulatory reporting pipeline processing 100M+ daily transactions.\n- Built ML platform integrating Snowflake Cortex, MLflow, SageMaker enabling 40 deployments annually.\n- Led data governance using Collibra achieving 95% data coverage and ISO 27001 compliance.\n- Managed team of 35 engineers with high retention and internal promotions.\n- Reduced Snowflake cost by $4.2M annually through optimization.\n- Implemented security and compliance for PCI-DSS, GLBA, CCPA.\n- Designed identity management using Okta SSO.\n\nEnvironment:\nSnowflake, dbt, Kafka, PySpark, MLflow, SageMaker, AWS, Collibra, Airflow, Terraform\n\n\nSENIOR DATA ENGINEER - LEAD\nCVS Health | Woonsocket, RI | Apr 2018 - Jan 2021\n\nClient: CVS Health\nDomain: Healthcare, Pharmacy Analytics\n\n- Built clinical data platform ingesting 2B+ patient records.\n- Developed real-time prescription monitoring system with sub-second latency.\n- Created NLP pipeline using spaCy and BERT reducing costs by $8M.\n- Designed Snowflake data sharing for secure collaboration.\n- Built 800+ dbt models supporting analytics.\n- Developed patient 360 data platform for 20M+ members.\n\nEnvironment:\nSnowflake, AWS Kinesis, Lambda, spaCy, BERT, dbt, Python, PySpark, Airflow\n\n\nDATA ENGINEER\nFedEx | Memphis, TN | Jul 2015 - Mar 2018\n\nClient: FedEx\nDomain: Logistics, IoT\n\n- Built analytics platform processing 15M+ daily shipment events.\n- Developed ML route optimization saving $25M annually.\n- Designed streaming system handling 50,000+ events per second.\n- Created data warehouse supporting multiple analytics domains.\n\nEnvironment:\nGCP BigQuery, Dataflow, Pub\/Sub, TensorFlow, Python, dbt, Looker\n\n\nDATA ANALYST \/ ETL DEVELOPER\nDeloitte Consulting | Chicago, IL | Sep 2013 - Jun 2015\n\n- Delivered 12 data engineering projects.\n- Developed Informatica ETL integrating SAP, Oracle, Salesforce.\n- Built Tableau dashboards for business insights.\n\nEnvironment:\nInformatica, SAP, Oracle, Tableau, SQL Server\n\n\nJUNIOR ETL DEVELOPER\nWipro Technologies | Hyderabad, India | Jun 2011 - Aug 2013\n\n- Built ETL pipelines processing 10M+ daily records.\n- Developed SQL procedures for data transformation.\n- Supported production ETL operations.\n\n\nKEY ACHIEVEMENTS\n\n- $35M TCO Savings from Snowflake migration\n- $25M fuel savings via ML optimization\n- $8M cost reduction using NLP automation\n- 100M+ events\/day real-time processing\n- 95% enterprise data governance coverage\n- 90% team retention\n\n\nTECHNICAL SKILLS\n\nArchitecture:\nData Mesh, Medallion Architecture, Lambda, Kappa, CQRS, Event Sourcing, Data Lakehouse\n\nData Warehouse:\nSnowflake, Redshift, BigQuery, Azure Synapse, Teradata, Oracle, SQL Server\n\nStreaming:\nKafka, Kinesis, Pub\/Sub, Flink, Spark Streaming, Kafka Streams\n\nML \/ AI:\nMLflow, Kubeflow, SageMaker, TensorFlow, PyTorch, spaCy, BERT\n\nGovernance:\nCollibra, Alation, Monte Carlo, DataHub, Apache Atlas, dbt Tests\n\nDevOps:\nGitHub Actions, Jenkins, Terraform, Docker, Kubernetes, Helm, ArgoCD\n\n\nCERTIFICATIONS\n\n- AWS Solutions Architect Professional\n- Snowflake SnowPro Advanced Data Engineer\n- GCP Professional Data Engineer\n- Azure Data Engineer Associate\n\n\nEDUCATION\n\nM.S. Computer Science\nUT Dallas | 2013\n\nB.Tech. Information Technology\nGujarat Technological University | 2011\n\n\nLINKS\n\nLinkedIn: linkedin.com\/in\/devrajpatel\nGitHub: github.com\/devrajpatel\nPortfolio: devrajpatel.com","label":[[0,12,"PERSON_NAME"],[14,38,"JOB_TITLE"],[41,62,"JOB_TITLE"],[65,68,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[76,101,"EMAIL"],[102,119,"PHONE_NUMBER"],[120,130,"LOCATION"],[131,158,"LINKEDIN"],[159,181,"GITHUB"],[183,186,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[303,306,"SKILL"],[481,493,"SKILL"],[516,525,"SKILL"],[527,530,"SKILL"],[536,542,"SKILL"],[555,560,"SKILL"],[607,620,"SKILL"],[727,738,"SKILL"],[744,754,"SKILL"],[792,796,"SKILL"],[800,806,"SKILL"],[840,864,"JOB_TITLE"],[865,876,"COMPANY_NAME"],[879,892,"LOCATION"],[895,913,"WORK_PERIOD"],[923,934,"COMPANY_NAME"],[1060,1069,"SKILL"],[1072,1082,"SKILL"],[1138,1141,"SKILL"],[1143,1150,"SKILL"],[1159,1167,"SKILL"],[1313,1316,"SKILL"],[1337,1353,"SKILL"],[1355,1361,"SKILL"],[1363,1373,"SKILL"],[1413,1428,"SKILL"],[1435,1444,"SKILL"],[1584,1594,"SKILL"],[1681,1688,"SKILL"],[1690,1694,"SKILL"],[1696,1700,"SKILL"],[1763,1772,"SKILL"],[1774,1777,"SKILL"],[1779,1784,"SKILL"],[1786,1793,"SKILL"],[1795,1801,"SKILL"],[1803,1812,"SKILL"],[1814,1817,"SKILL"],[1819,1827,"SKILL"],[1829,1836,"SKILL"],[1838,1847,"SKILL"],[1850,1877,"JOB_TITLE"],[1878,1888,"COMPANY_NAME"],[1891,1905,"LOCATION"],[1908,1916,"START_DATE"],[1919,1927,"END_DATE"],[1937,1947,"COMPANY_NAME"],[1956,1966,"JOB_TITLE"],[1968,1986,"JOB_TITLE"],[2206,2216,