{"id":18,"text":"VENKY\nPrincipal React Developer\nEmail: [react.architect@techmail.com](mailto:react.architect@techmail.com)\nPhone: +1 555-555-5555\nLocation: USA\nLinkedIn: linkedin.com\/in\/reactarchitect\nGitHub: github.com\/reactarchitect\n\n---\n\nPROFESSIONAL SUMMARY\n\nPrincipal React \/ Frontend Engineer with 20+ years of experience building large-scale web applications, enterprise portals, SaaS platforms, and consumer products. Expert in React ecosystem, UI architecture, performance optimization, accessibility, and design systems. Proven leader in frontend modernization and migration of legacy systems to modern React-based architectures. Extensive experience across banking, healthcare, telecom, retail, and SaaS domains. Strong background in cloud platforms, DevOps, and secure frontend engineering practices.\n\n---\n\nCORE COMPETENCIES\n\nReact Architecture\nFrontend System Design\nMicro-Frontend Architecture\nUI Performance Optimization\nEnterprise UI Platforms\nDesign Systems\nAccessibility (WCAG)\nResponsive and Mobile-First Design\nState Management\nAPI Integration\nSecurity Best Practices\nCI\/CD for Frontend\nTesting Automation\nLegacy Modernization\nCloud-Native UI\nTechnical Leadership\nMentoring and Code Reviews\nStakeholder Collaboration\n\n---\n\nTECHNICAL SKILLS\n\nFrontend: React, React Hooks, Redux, Redux Toolkit, MobX, Zustand, Recoil, Next.js, Remix, Gatsby, Vue, Angular\nStyling: HTML5, CSS3, SCSS, LESS, Styled Components, Tailwind, Material UI, Chakra UI, Ant Design\nLanguages: JavaScript, TypeScript\nBuild Tools: Webpack, Vite, Rollup, Parcel, Babel\nPackage Managers: NPM, Yarn, PNPM\nState Management: Redux Saga, Redux Thunk, React Query, SWR\nAPIs: REST, GraphQL, Apollo, Relay\nTesting: Jest, React Testing Library, Cypress, Playwright, Selenium\nPerformance: Code Splitting, Lazy Loading, Tree Shaking, Memoization, Virtualization\nSecurity: XSS Prevention, CSRF, OAuth2, JWT, SSO\nAccessibility: WCAG 2.1, ARIA\nCloud\/DevOps: Docker, Kub