oyment\n• 90% Retention — Team leadership success\n\n\nTECHNICAL EXPERTISE\n\nArchitecture:\nData Mesh, Data Lake, Lambda Architecture, Kappa Architecture, Medallion Architecture, CQRS, Event Sourcing\n\nData Warehousing:\nSnowflake, Redshift, BigQuery, Azure Synapse, Teradata, Oracle, SQL Server, Hive, Presto, Trino\n\nStreaming:\nKafka, Kinesis, Pub\/Sub, Event Hubs, Flink, Spark Streaming, Kafka Streams, NiFi\n\nML \/ AI:\nMLflow, Kubeflow, SageMaker, Snowflake Cortex, Vertex AI, Azure ML, TensorFlow, PyTorch, spaCy, BERT\n\nGovernance:\nCollibra, Alation, Monte Carlo, DataHub, Apache Atlas, Great Expectations, dbt Tests, Soda\n\nDevOps:\nGitHub Actions, GitLab CI\/CD, Jenkins, Terraform, Pulumi, Docker, Kubernetes, Helm, ArgoCD\n\n\nEDUCATION\n\nM.S. Computer Science\nUniversity of Texas at Dallas | 2013\n\nB.Tech. Information Technology\nGujarat Technological University | 2011\n\n\nCERTIFICATIONS\n\n• AWS Solutions Architect Professional\n• Snowflake SnowPro Advanced Data Engineer\n• GCP Professional Data Engineer\n• Azure Data Engineer Associate (DP-203)\n\n\nSPEAKING & PUBLICATIONS\n\n• Strata Data Conference 2023 — Keynote: Data Mesh at Scale\n• Snowflake Summit 2022 — Workshop: Cortex AI for Enterprises\n• DataCouncil Austin 2021 — Talk: Real-Time Compliance Pipelines\n\n\nLINKS\n\nLinkedIn: linkedin.com\/in\/devrajpatel\nGitHub: github.com\/devrajpatel\nPortfolio: devrajpatel.com","label":[[0,12,"PERSON_NAME"],[13,38,"JOB_TITLE"],[40,61,"JOB_TITLE"],[64,67,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[82,107,"EMAIL"],[115,132,"PHONE_NUMBER"],[142,153,"LOCATION"],[164,191,"LINKEDIN"],[200,222,"GITHUB"],[243,267,"JOB_TITLE"],[272,293,"JOB_TITLE"],[299,301,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[400,410,"SKILL"],[416,425,"SKILL"],[448,456,"SKILL"],[457,470,"SKILL"],[493,502,"SKILL"],[504,507,"SKILL"],[513,519,"SKILL"],[530,536,"SKILL"],[760,771,"SKILL"],[777,787,"SKILL"],[822,833,"COMPANY_NAME"],[836,860,"JOB_TITLE"],[861,880,"WORK_PERIOD"],[882,895,"LOCATION"],[977,987,"SKILL"],[992,1001,"SKILL"],[100