s on Azure\" — Microsoft Build 2023  \n\n--------------------------------------------------\nTECHNICAL SKILLS\n--------------------------------------------------\n\nStreaming:\nKafka, Apache Flink, Spark Streaming, AWS Kinesis, Azure Event Hubs, Kafka Streams, NiFi\n\nLakehouse:\nDatabricks Delta Lake, Apache Iceberg, Apache Hudi, AWS Lake Formation, Azure ADLS, Trino, Presto\n\nData Warehousing:\nSnowflake, Azure Synapse, BigQuery, Redshift, Databricks SQL, Apache Druid, ClickHouse\n\nLanguages:\nPython, Scala, Java, SQL, PySpark, Go, Bash, JavaScript, TypeScript\n\nTools:\ndbt, Terraform, Helm\n\nInfrastructure \/ DevOps:\nKubernetes, Docker, Helm, Terraform, Pulumi, GitHub Actions, ArgoCD, Prometheus, Grafana, Datadog\n\n--------------------------------------------------\nCERTIFICATIONS\n--------------------------------------------------\n\n• Microsoft Certified: Azure Data Engineer Associate  \n• Azure Solutions Architect Expert  \n• Confluent Certified Developer for Apache Kafka (CCDAK)  \n• Databricks Certified Data Engineer Professional  \n• Snowflake SnowPro Core  \n• Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA)\n\n--------------------------------------------------\nEDUCATION\n--------------------------------------------------\n\nM.S. Computer Science (Distributed Systems)\nUniversity of Washington, Seattle | 2013\n\nB.Tech. Computer Science\nJNTU Hyderabad, India | 2011\n\n--------------------------------------------------\nLINKS\n--------------------------------------------------\n\nLinkedIn: linkedin.com\/in\/venkatreddy  \nGitHub: github.com\/vkreddy  \nConfluent: confluent.io\/hub\/vkreddy","label":[[0,20,"PERSON_NAME"],[21,43,"JOB_TITLE"],[66,69,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[84,112,"EMAIL"],[119,137,"PHONE_NUMBER"],[148,157,"LOCATION"],[168,195,"LINKEDIN"],[204,222,"GITHUB"],[236,239,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[396,419,"JOB_TITLE"],[480,490,"SKILL"],[529,544,"SKILL"],[547,552,"SKILL"],[555,558,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[628,633,"SKILL"],[639,646,"SKILL"],[658,670,"SKILL"],[670,