{"id":51,"text":"ANIL K C\nSENIOR FULL STACK DEVELOPER\n LinkedIn | Email: siranilworkspace92@gmail.com | Mobile: 260-255-4858\n________________________________________\nPROFESSIONAL SUMMARY\n•\tSenior Full Stack Developer with 11 years of experience in delivering enterprise scale applications using Java, J2EE, and Spring Boot, supporting complex business workflows across multiple domains and platforms.\n•\tEngineered resilient payment platforms by designing multi-currency transaction flows, fraud detection pipelines, and secure APIs using Java, Spring Boot, Kafka, OAuth2, and SSL\/TLS, while ensuring observability, fault isolation, and compliance across globally distributed banking systems.\n•\tRevitalized high-traffic retail pricing ecosystems by delivering responsive user interfaces and stable backend services through React, Spring Boot, REST, and JSON, enabling accurate promotions, consistent API behavior, and scalable workflows supporting nationwide retail operations.\n•\tStrengthened regulated pharmacy and healthcare platforms by modernizing legacy processing pipelines with Java, Spring Framework, Hibernate, and JPA, improving prescription reliability, data integrity, and transactional consistency across enterprise healthcare systems.\n•\tArchitected scalable service layers by structuring modular business logic, persistence boundaries, and transactional flows using Spring MVC, Spring AOP, Hibernate, and JDBC, ensuring maintainable codebases aligned with enterprise performance and reliability expectations.\n•\tDelivered secure system integrations by designing contract-driven interfaces with REST, GraphQL, SOAP, JSON, and XML, enabling reliable communication between internal platforms, financial partners, and external enterprise services.\n•\tImplemented distributed microservice ecosystems using Microservices Architecture, Spring Boot, Micronaut, and Dapr, standardizing service invocation, retries, pub\/sub messaging, and state management while isolating busines