{"id":81,"text":"YAMINI\nSenior Java Full Stack Developer\n\nEmail: yamini2@gmail.com\nPhone: +1 (901)-625-1764\nLinkedIn: linkedin.com\/in\/yamini\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\nPROFESSIONAL SUMMARY\n------------------------------------------------------------\nSenior Java Full Stack Developer with 11+ years of experience working on enterprise applications across healthcare, banking, retail, and aviation domains. Experienced in analysis, development, integration, deployment, and production support across the SDLC. Skilled in building scalable, high-performance microservices and cloud-native applications using Java, Spring Boot, and modern DevOps practices.\n\nExpertise in RESTful APIs, distributed systems, AI\/ML integrations, and secure application development using OAuth2, JWT, and Spring Security. Strong experience across AWS, Azure, and GCP with containerization and orchestration using Docker and Kubernetes. Proven ability to lead teams, mentor developers, and deliver enterprise-grade solutions.\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\nTECHNICAL SKILLS\n------------------------------------------------------------\nBackend & Core: Java (8\/11\/17\/21), J2EE, Spring Boot, Spring MVC, Spring Data, Hibernate, JDBC, REST APIs, SOAP, Microservices  \nFrontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, TypeScript, Angular, React.js, Bootstrap, jQuery  \nDatabases: Oracle, PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQL Server, MongoDB, Cassandra  \nMessaging: Kafka, RabbitMQ, JMS, AWS SQS  \nSecurity: Spring Security, OAuth2, JWT  \nDevOps & Tools: Docker, Kubernetes, OpenShift, Terraform, Jenkins, GitHub Actions, Maven, Ant  \nCloud: AWS, Azure, GCP  \nTesting: JUnit, TestNG, Mockito, Cucumber, Cypress, JMeter, Postman  \nOthers: Git, GitHub, GitLab, SVN, Linux, UNIX, Windows  \n\n------------------------------------------------------------\nPROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nUnitedHealth Group | S