ty.\n- Worked with PostgreSQL and GCP Cloud SQL.\n- Implemented messaging using RabbitMQ.\n- Deployed applications using Docker and Kubernetes.\n\nEnvironment: Java, Spring Boot, GCP, PostgreSQL, RabbitMQ, Docker, Kubernetes\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nRamco Systems | Backend Developer\nAugust 2014 – October 2015 | Chennai, India\n- Developed enterprise applications using Java, Spring MVC, and Hibernate.\n- Built SOAP and REST services for system integrations.\n- Worked with SQL Server databases and optimized queries.\n- Applied design patterns for scalable architecture.\n\nEnvironment: Java, Spring MVC, Hibernate, SQL Server, SOAP, JUnit\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\nEDUCATION\n------------------------------------------------------------\nBachelor of Technology in Computer Science  \nMLWE College  \nJune 2010 – July 2014\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\nADDITIONAL SKILLS\n------------------------------------------------------------\n- Microservices Architecture & Design Patterns  \n- AI\/ML Integration (LLMs, Spring AI)  \n- Cloud-Native Development  \n- Performance Optimization & Monitoring  \n- Agile \/ Scrum \/ SDLC  \n\n\n------------------------------------------------------------","label":[[0,6,"PERSON_NAME"],[7,39,"JOB_TITLE"],[47,65,"EMAIL"],[73,90,"PHONE_NUMBER"],[101,123,"LINKEDIN"],[268,300,"JOB_TITLE"],[306,309,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[372,382,"SKILL"],[384,391,"SKILL"],[393,399,"SKILL"],[405,421,"SKILL"],[448,459,"SKILL"],[461,472,"SKILL"],[474,484,"SKILL"],[520,524,"SKILL"],[573,587,"SKILL"],[591,616,"SKILL"],[623,627,"SKILL"],[629,640,"SKILL"],[653,660,"SKILL"],[685,697,"SKILL"],[720,738,"SKILL"],[781,787,"SKILL"],[789,792,"SKILL"],[840,843,"SKILL"],[845,850,"SKILL"],[856,860,"SKILL"],[906,913,"SKILL"],[917,927,"SKILL"],[959,976,"SKILL"],[1174,1179,"SKILL"],[1193,1197,"SKILL"],[1199,1210,"SKILL"],[1212,1222,"SKILL"],[1224,1235,"SKILL"],[1237,1246,"SK