ro-touch infrastructure provisioning\n  → Reduced time from 4 days to 25 minutes\n\n• Automated DR testing (Chaos Engineering)\n  → Fixed 9 critical issues\n\n• Secrets management overhaul\n  → Zero credential incidents\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\nCERTIFICATIONS\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n• AWS DevOps Engineer – Professional\n• AWS Solutions Architect – Associate\n• Certified Kubernetes Administrator (CKA)\n• Terraform Associate\n• AWS Cloud Practitioner\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\nEDUCATION\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nB.Tech – Computer Science\nJNTU Hyderabad | 2015\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\nTOOLS & TECHNOLOGIES\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nAWS, Azure, GCP, Kubernetes, Terraform, Docker, Jenkins, GitHub, \nPrometheus, Grafana, ELK, Python, Bash\n\n------------------------------------------------------------\nPUBLICATIONS & CONFERENCES\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\n• Speaker – AWS Community Day Hyderabad (2023)\n• Article – Terraform at Enterprise Scale (15K+ views)\n• Tech Talk – Zero Trust Networking in AWS\n• Open Source – terraform-aws-eks-platform (400+ stars)","label":[[0,5,"PERSON_NAME"],[6,51,"JOB_TITLE"],[53,73,"LOCATION"],[75,101,"EMAIL"],[104,119,"PHONE_NUMBER"],[120,148,"LINKEDIN"],[307,330,"JOB_TITLE"],[336,339,"EXPERIANCE_YEARS"],[380,390,"SKILL"],[406,427,"SKILL"],[431,434,"SKILL"],[460,481,"SKILL"],[499,518,"SKILL"],[535,542,"SKILL"],[553,564,"SKILL"],[620,631,"SKILL"],[646,666,"SKILL"],[672,682,"SKILL"],[712,716,"SKILL"],[718,728,"SKILL"],[733,744,"SKILL"],[806,821,"SKILL"],[828,836,"SKILL"],[837,849,"SKILL"],[1059,1083,"SKILL"],[1085,1107,"SKILL"],[1109,1122,"SKILL"],[1126,1146,"SKILL"],[1146,1165,"SKILL"],[1169,1180,"SKILL"],[1182,1185,"SKILL"],[1187,1204,"SKILL"],[1206,1223,"SKILL"],[1225,124